T1  - A hybrid methodology for assessing hydropower plants under flexible operations: Leveraging experimental data and machine learning techniques
AU  - Amini, Ali
AU  - Rey-Mermet, Samuel
AU  - Crettenand, Steve
AU  - Münch-Alligné, Cécile
JO  - Applied Energy
VL  - 383
SP  - 125402
